2013-11-15 - Version 1.0 released

This is the first public release of pgCluu, that is a packaging of the tools I
use every day to collect statistics and build reports of PostgreSQL Cluster for
performances auditing.

At this time it report everything that is helpfull for a PostgreSQL Cluster
performance auditing, but still need addtional information about queries from
pg_stat_statement. This will comes in next release.

